folder: Myrtle Avenue & Union Turnpike, Queens, NY
text:
Myrtle Ave., north side, between Union Turnpike and 81st Road, showing a roadhouse belonging to Welz and Zerweck, the brewer. These buildings were demolished prior to 1929.

May 1923.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
title: Queens: Myrtle Avenue - Union Turnpike
